snippet.title: ABYSS X ZERO Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Announcing: ABYSS X ZERO

Studio Pixel Punk's new game

A 3D Metroidvania with carefully crafted dungeons and expressive low poly visuals. Take control of two different characters, both legendary heroes with unique abilities, fated to battle each other.

We're a two person team, and the project is still very early in development.

Support us by wishlisting ABYSS X ZERO on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2872300/ABYSS_X_ZERO/
